import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Link, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from "./pages/Home"
import Survey from "./pages/Survey"


ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <Router>
      <Route exact path="/">
        <Home />
      </Route>
      <Route path="/survey">
        <Survey />
      </Route>
    </Router>
  </React.StrictMode>
)
